{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":10,"day":1}],"page_start":5,"page_end":5,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"边防战士想念毛主席","authors":["毛健民"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：在我们边防连队的广播室"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放着一台“东方红”收音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每天早晨，我们在军号声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中醒来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就听见从北京传来的消"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我禁不住轻轻地喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您好啊，北京！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您好啊，毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：您好啊，北京！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：您好啊，北京！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您好呀，毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：毛主席住在北京城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的连队住在西南边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"境，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远隔着江水条条、高山重"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的心啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却时时刻刻向着——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的领袖毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮丽的首都北京城！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：远隔着江水条条、高山重"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高原的边防战士啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想念着毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想念着北京！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：北京！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们祖国的心脏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们心中的红太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时刻带在我们身上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远刻在我们心上！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：我们守卫着西南边疆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就象站立在毛主席的身"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：还记得：——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们连初来边疆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雪弥漫，四野苍茫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有一棵树，没有半间房。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我脑子里画了个大问号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道这就是我们安家的地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指导员好象看穿了我们的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心思，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他亲切地对我们讲："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“同志，这里是祖国的大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里是祖国的边疆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席才派我们到这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为祖国人民站岗。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的话象一道火光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一下子把我的心底照亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们全连苦战了一个月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就修起了现在的营房。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：毛主席就是胜利！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席就是力量！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：每当夜深人静，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我站在岗哨上凝神静听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里山川已经睡去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国内地又该有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少个窗口传出催眠的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声，多少孩子正做着美丽的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时，一种庄严的责任"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽然涌上我的心头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对高耸的雪山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺骨的寒风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心啊，好象钢水在沸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我精神振奋、睁大眼睛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：哨兵的眼睛最亮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哨兵的眼睛最明！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：在下哨的路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我脚步放得轻轻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只怕把酣睡的山川惊醒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着北方的群山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透过千山万水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见中南海的一座平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍然灯火通明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席还在工作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不禁轻轻地喊出声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，就在此刻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我面前冰雪顿时融化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凛冽的寒风也变得不冷！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：毛主席给哨兵带来温暖！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席就是春风！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：那是一个星期六的下午，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们学习了毛主席的文"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"章，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚上放映《国庆十周年》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的电影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看见毛主席站在天安门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我回到宿舍还心潮汹涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心头浮现许多联想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想念着毛主席，想念着北"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一夜，我多么幸福呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦见毛主席来到营房！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席来到咱们营房！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：毛主席穿一双布鞋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一身灰布衣裳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他微笑着向我走来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不知道说什么好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激动得泪水涌满了眼眶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席抚摸着我的头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又拉拉我的手问："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“小同志，今年多大了？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“报告主席，今年刚满十"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：刚满十九正是好年龄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象桃李初开，象太阳东升"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：主席呵，如果您还问我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就会响亮地回答："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我愿在西藏住上一辈子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哨所就是我的家。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：这里是："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的地，祖国的天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的大门，战斗的前线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们愿意永远当一名哨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终生为祖国把岗站。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：毛主席满意地笑啦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他让我们好好工作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好好地守在祖国边境。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我高兴地从梦中笑醒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一看呀，太阳东升，满屋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通红。合：呵，毛主席就是太阳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席就是光明！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：在我们边防连队的广播室"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放着一台“东方红”收音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：每天早晨，我们在军号声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中醒来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就听见从北京传来的消"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：我禁不住轻轻地喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您好啊，北京！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您好啊，毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：您好啊，北京！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您好啊，毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：您好啊，北京！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您好啊，毛主席！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}